/*
 *  CRYPTOGRAPHY 101
 * 
 *  OK                  WEAK     BROKEN
 *  ------------------  ------   ------
 *  ECDHE > ECDH > DHE
 *  ECDSA > RSA
 *  GCM > CCM           > CBC   > ECB
 *  SHA2                > SHA1  > MD5
 *  AES                 > 3DES  > DES
 *  CHACHA                      > RC4
 */

